data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. MOTIVATED SELLER & a $10,000 Incentive at closing for Pre-Paids & Closing Costs!!! This UNIQUE, CRYSTAL BEACH GEM  with 3bd/2ba, 1,529 Sq. Ft. is truly one-of-a-kind!  It sits on TWO lots,  (.27acre ttl), and offers 2 paver patios with thoughtful, tropical landscaping, has 1 detached garage and 1 shed. Entering into your new home you’ll be greeted by a generous, cozy foyer/entrance room.  To the right is your grand entrance into the sprawling great room adorned with high coffer ceilings. Beautiful built in shelving in great room and dining rooms. Up the beautiful staircase you’ll find 2 bedrooms, with a balcony that overlooks the great room. Walk-in closet in Master, 1 1/2 bathrooms.  Downstairs passed the great room you’ll be welcomed into the country kitchen, laundry and storage room and screened in lanai, upstairs outdoor balcony off the hall.  Home boasts large office overlooking yard and gardens with plenty of storage, windows and natural light into third bedroom or bonus room. Two Fireplaces, one in master bedroom, one in great room. Original refinished Hardwood floors throughout. Wainscoting is beautiful!  NEW ROOF in 2021! Hardwood floors refinished one year ago. It’s a MUST SEE!   Seller has 4 Point Inspection available for you to use dated7/5/2023!  This is your rare opportunity to own a 100+ year old, charming home with tons of character in the highly sought after Crystal Beach Community! Once you arrive, you’ll know you are finally home! The Crystal Beach community is on the gulf side of Florida. Step onto the sidewalk and you can see the gulf just 1 1/2 blocks away. Then turn around and walk 1/2 block to the Pinellas Trail. This property is on the highest elevation in Crystal Beach. Therefore it does not require flood insurance.  Make it yours Today!
